[Course_Description]
Learn how to perfect exposure and color as well as unlock details in your raw files in Adobe Lightroom. This class covers several important tools as well as hidden options for taking your raw files to the next level. Take your time and work your way through each lesson to discover new imaging superpowers. Discover how to make basic adjustments, apply tone curves, add detail, perform split toning and lens corrections, add creative effects, merge panoramas and HDR images, and use profiles and presets. Instructor Rich Harrington also shows how to use advanced Lightroom controls such as gradient adjustments and brush-based local adjustments. This course was created by Rhed Pixel. We are pleased to offer this training in our library.